column1: Medicare Advantage Monthly Capitation Rates for 2011 for All Plans Except PACE Plans
2011 Rates are identical to the 2010 rates in accordance with Section 1102 of the Health Care & Education Affordability Reconciliation Act of 2010.
Note: 1. The 2010 risk rates reflect an adjustment of 1.001 for budget neutrality.
2. ESRD rates are shown after the deduction of user fee of $5.25.
3. All rates include MIPPA IME deduction.
